<item>
            <title>[HBASE-16547] hbase-archetype-builder shell scripts assume bash is installed in /bin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-16547</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s no guarantee UNIX systems will have bash installed in /bin. HBase builds fail for me on FreeBSD. The hbase-archetype-builder scripts do not use any bash features so let&apos;s specify &apos;/bin/sh&apos; as interpreter instead. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
